videos.description: Michigan gives up the longest play of their season with an 80-yard touchdown run to Isaih Pacheco, who ties the game at 7-7.
videos.headline: Rutgers RB Pacheco ties it with 80-yard TD

videos.description: Michigan goes up 7-0 on a 1-yard touchdown for Karan Higdon.
videos.headline: Higdon gives Michigan early lead

videos.description: Karan Higdon plows through the line for his second 1-yard touchdown of the afternoon, putting Michigan up 14-7.
videos.headline: Higdon busts through for 2nd TD

videos.description: QB Shea Patterson fires a 36-yard touchdown to a wide-open Nico Collins to give Michigan a two-score lead.
videos.headline: Rutgers' blown coverage gives Michigan wide-open TD

videos.description: Michigan QB Shea Patterson gets great blocking during a scramble before firing a touchdown on the move to Oliver Martin.
videos.headline: Patterson scrambles around pocket to fire off-balance TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson throws a back-shoulder fade to Nico Collins for his second touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Collins snags back-shoulder catch for 2nd TD
